videos.description: Jordan Bowden blocks the dunk attempt by Villanova's Omari Spellman going down the lane.
videos.headline: Tennessee's Bowden denies Nova dunk attempt at rim

videos.description: Mikal Bridges goes to the hoop and makes the layup and gets the foul call.
videos.headline: Villanova's Bridges drives through hard contact for and-1

videos.description: Grant Williams drives baseline and shows off the one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Tennessee's Williams throws down one-handed slam

videos.description: Wildcats guard Donte DiVincenzo drills the 3-pointer in transition to tie the game after being down by 12 at halftime.
videos.headline: DiVincenzo's 3-pointer caps off 14-2 run by Villanova

videos.description: Villanova guard Donte DiVincenzo comes up with the steal and goes the other way for the dunk.
videos.headline: DiVincenzo gets steal, shows off vertical on dunk

videos.description: Tennessee forward Admiral Schofield drills a 3-pointer from the wing to cut the Villanova lead to 79-76.
videos.headline: Schofield 3-pointer cuts Nova lead to 3 points

videos.description: Jalen Brunson scores 25 points to help No. 5 Villanova stave off Tennessee.
videos.headline: Nova's defensive tempo leads to second-half surge
